  <data key="d0">"IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The category of this image feature block is 'person'. The entity features are as follows:Person Features:- **Gender:** Appears to be female.- **Hairstyle:** Long, dark hair, seemingly pulled back or styled, visible from the side profile.- **Clothing:** Wearing a dark, short-sleeved top (possibly a t-shirt or athletic jersey) and dark shorts. There appears to be a lighter colored band or stripe on the upper right arm.- **Facial Expression:** The face is mostly obscured as the person is in a side profile with the head tilted downwards. No clear expression is discernible.- **Age:** Appears to be an adult or older youth.- **Posture:** The person is in an athletic stance, leaning forward with knees slightly bent. Both arms are extended forward and slightly upwards, with hands together, suggesting an action like receiving or hitting a ball (e.g., in volleyball).- **Overall Impression:** The pose indicates active participation in a sport or physical activity. The image is black and white."</data>
